{"tid":1230913,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"毅進仔好失禮，毅進仔EQ低","createTime":"2019-06-16T10:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T01:01:02.000Z","uid":75211,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d3c8746d0d037d0450d73f347ac5ee9b67c5c78f","tid":1230913,"uid":75211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:40:04.000Z","msg":"所以話讀得毅進個班 <br />\n其實真係社會垃圾中垃圾<br />\n你係讀到書一早讀左上大學<br />\n洗撚靠啲旁門左道去爭學位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係我講你班垃圾<br />\n係我識個啲濕鳩廢閪同學<br />\n一半讀毅進大部份每日返學都打卡<br />\nPost 上ig 十有八九唔係打機就訓教<br />\n讀唔成書又要逃避返工呢個現實<br />\n真係社會中嘅渣滓 讀得上去個個都讀啦<br />\n毅進仔廢柴垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：歡迎補充"},{"pid":"2a7d0db1d6ea94d009d383e4772b513add396512","tid":1230913,"uid":75211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:41:35.000Z","msg":"知自己讀唔成書<br />\n出來做左2-3年野儲錢<br />\n呢家開左間小企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班毅進仔仲諗緊自己前途 廢撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0dc2da8b2b79f2422465241f0224a7712d7438d","tid":1230913,"uid":75211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:42:39.000Z","msg":"來辯呀 毅進傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1242457ceef70887e76bc6784d6c822e4505cecd","tid":1230913,"uid":75211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:44:49.000Z","msg":"屌我未傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6297417c02a9ed2257c6745efe10a80de13c48","tid":1230913,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:46:54.000Z","msg":"5條2都冇 -&gt; 讀毅進等於5條2 -&gt; 拎住毅進先有機會讀副學位-&gt; 但係副學位GPA唔過2.5又係入唔返學士<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aafa71ad2c9b65d1c1bc9fd7c5fa64c1a0cbfa94","tid":123091